  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/325bd2d53b02ec57066962c691287c5b.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Get yourself comfortable! <br>You are tasked with taking care of an old Lighthouse and this small island is now your new home.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/c7d0c7e71b48f512c5daed9729f740c3.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Hunt for fish or seagulls for food or grow your own vegetables by repairing the farm. <br>Chop down trees, mine for minerals and upgrade your tools.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/a05b0e6739d7dafe6c148237ceb36d29.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Time wears down the old Lighthouse, figure out how it's mechanisms work to make sure they work again. <br>Sometimes you'll need materials, sometimes you'll just need to be smart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/759e629dc2264a08a335b74dba9a7a2d.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Sail to different islands with your boat and discover their secrets and collect additional resources.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/325bd2d53b02ec57066962c691287c5b.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Get yourself comfortable! <br>You are tasked with taking care of an old Lighthouse and this small island is now your new home.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/c7d0c7e71b48f512c5daed9729f740c3.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Hunt for fish or seagulls for food or grow your own vegetables by repairing the farm. <br>Chop down trees, mine for minerals and upgrade your tools.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/a05b0e6739d7dafe6c148237ceb36d29.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Time wears down the old Lighthouse, figure out how it's mechanisms work to make sure they work again. <br>Sometimes you'll need materials, sometimes you'll just need to be smart.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2023050/extras/759e629dc2264a08a335b74dba9a7a2d.avif?t=1747806801\" width=612 height=86 /></span><br><br>Sail to different islands with your boat and discover their secrets and collect additional resources.",
